T1  - THE LOW-POWERED LEADER CONFRONTS A MESSY PROBLEM: A TEST OF FIEDLER'S THEORY
AU  - Hovey, Donald E.
Y1  - 1974/06/01
PY  - 1974
DA  - 1974/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/254989
